text: Dominique Brieussel (born 7 October 1962) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Enghien-les-Bains
